Pope <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Benedict XVI</ENAMEX> began his <ENAMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">first</ENAMEX> visit to the lands of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Islam</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Ankara</ENAMEX> .
