A dialogue between the various cultures and between the <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</ENAMEX> religions of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Christianity</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Islam</ENAMEX> .
